@authToken = {{login.response.body.data.token}}
@id = e534fd37-641a-44f2-9ad8-4dad7bf431d9

### Auth - Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "superadmin@example.com",
