### Permissions - List
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Permissions - Get By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Permissions - Create
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "reports.read"
}

### Permissions - Update
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "reports.read"
}

### Permissions - Delete
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/permissions/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
